high_descs: Turn right to face the tomatoes on the counter.
Pick up the left tomato on the counter.
Turn left, head across the kitchen, turn left to face the mike on the counter.
Heat the tomato in the mike.
Bring the heated tomato to the sink on the left.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the leftmost tomato off of the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the microwave.
Microwave the tomato for a couple seconds, then take it out of the microwave and close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the heated tomato in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: cook the tomato in the oven and take it out
turn left and head to the sink
place the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato in the sink
